Source: jackbridge
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Maintainer: pistomp <pistomp@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), git
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: jackbridge
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, jack2-pistomp,
 jack-example-tools, iproute2
Description: netJACK2 client for DAW recording over Ethernet
 Installs the pi-side JackBridge service: 6 helper scripts under
 /usr/local/libexec/jackbridge/ plus pi-stomp-jackbridge.service.
 The service is on-demand only (not enabled at boot); the LCD UI
 starts/stops it via systemctl.